Package: HerdDynamics
Title: Enables Livestock Demographic Modelling
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Nicholas", "Triozzi", , "triozzi@ucsb.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1856-7449"))
Description: HerdDynamics can be used to project age and sex structured 
    population changes of livestock herds. Input parameters include age- and sex-
    specific offtake rates, fertility (i.e., parturitions and prolificacy), and 
    mortality. Additional tools allow for adjustment factors to be generated to 
    reach a steady state of herd growth.
